{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Formation Claude IA pour Consultants & Formateurs Solo{% endblock %}
{% block titleSuffix %} | Instant IA{% endblock %}
{% block description %}La méthode pas-à-pas pour transformer Claude en ton bras droit en 14 jours. Pour consultants, formateurs et solopreneurs non-tech. Garantie 14j.{% endblock %}

{# On override le header par défaut de base.html.twig pour la home —
   le header reste le même, mais on garde la possibilité de switch vers
   une version "scrolled" sur la home (à venir Sprint 2.x). #}

{% block body %}

{# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   SECTION 1 — HERO KINETIC (style Relancya : dark + grid + mot qui change + card mockup glass)
   ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
<section class="hero-kinetic" id="top">

    {# Bulles flottantes décoratives autour du hero #}
    <span class="floating-badge floating-badge--top-left" aria-hidden="true">Email rédigé auto</span>
    <span class="floating-badge floating-badge--top-right" aria-hidden="true">CR généré · 1 min</span>
    <span class="floating-badge floating-badge--bottom-left" aria-hidden="true">Propal envoyée</span>
    <span class="floating-badge floating-badge--bottom-right" aria-hidden="true">Scénario activé auto</span>

    <div class="hero-kinetic-content">
        <div class="hero-kinetic-grid">

            {# Colonne gauche #}
            <div class="hero-kinetic-left">
                <p class="eyebrow-ds" style="color: var(--color-gold-300);">
                    Formation pour consultants &amp; formateurs solo
                </p>

                <h1 class="hero-kinetic-headline">
                    Transforme Claude en ton <em>bras droit</em><br>
                    en 14 jours.
                </h1>

                <p class="hero-kinetic-sub">
                    La méthode <strong>pas-à-pas</strong> pour consultants et formateurs solo qui veulent
                    récupérer <strong>10h/semaine</strong>
                    <span class="dim">— sans devenir tech, sans coder, sans 200 prompts à apprendre par cœur.</span>
                </p>

                <div class="hero-kinetic-actions">
                    <a href="/formation-claude-consultant"
                       data-controller="magnetic-button"
                       class="hero-kinetic-btn hero-kinetic-btn--primary">
                        Je veux mon Système Claude <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="#lead-magnet" class="hero-kinetic-link">
                        Découvre 3 Agents IA gratuits <span aria-hidden="true">↓</span>
                    </a>
                </div>

                <ul class="hero-kinetic-badges" aria-label="Garanties de la formation">
                    <li><span aria-hidden="true">⭐</span> 4,9/5</li>
                    <li><span aria-hidden="true">🎁</span> 14j satisfait/remboursé</li>
                    <li><span aria-hidden="true">🇫🇷</span> 100% en français</li>
                    <li><span aria-hidden="true">📱</span> Vidéos courtes 3-5 min</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            {# Colonne droite — mockup glassmorphism #}
            <div class="hero-kinetic-right">
                <div class="hero-mockup">

                    <div class="hero-mockup-header">
                        <span class="hero-mockup-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" fill="none">
                                <path d="M13 2L4.5 13.5H11.5L10.5 22L19.5 10.5H12.5L13 2Z" fill="currentColor"/>
                            </svg>
                        </span>
                        <div class="hero-mockup-title">
                            <h3>Tableau de bord — Tes Agents Claude</h3>
                            <p>Mis à jour il y a 2 min</p>
                        </div>
                        <span class="hero-mockup-status">3 actifs</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="hero-mockup-row">
                        <span class="hero-mockup-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E8C547, #C5A044);">📧</span>
                        <span>
                            <span class="name">Agent Inbox</span>
                            <span class="meta">12 emails triés aujourd'hui</span>
                        </span>
                        <span class="stat">4h</span>
                        <span class="hero-mockup-tag hero-mockup-tag--active">Actif</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="hero-mockup-row">
                        <span class="hero-mockup-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6B877B, #3D564B); color: #FAF8F4;">🎙</span>
                        <span>
                            <span class="name">Agent Mission</span>
                            <span class="meta">CR généré · il y a 5 min</span>
                        </span>
                        <span class="stat">3h</span>
                        <span class="hero-mockup-tag hero-mockup-tag--running">En cours</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="hero-mockup-row">
                        <span class="hero-mockup-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A6B52, #064E3B); color: #FAF8F4;">📋</span>
                        <span>
                            <span class="name">Agent Propal</span>
                            <span class="meta">Acme Corp · réglée ✓</span>
                        </span>
                        <span class="stat">3h</span>
                        <span class="hero-mockup-tag hero-mockup-tag--done">Envoyée</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="hero-mockup-stats">
                        <div>
                            <span class="num"
                                  data-controller="counter-animation"
                                  data-counter-animation-target-value="11"
                                  data-counter-animation-suffix-value="h">0h</span>
                            <span class="label">Gagnées / sem</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="num"
                                  data-controller="counter-animation"
                                  data-counter-animation-target-value="3">0</span>
                            <span class="label">Agents actifs</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="num"
                                  data-controller="counter-animation"
                                  data-counter-animation-target-value="14">0</span>
                            <span class="label">Jours sprint</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

{# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   SECTION 2 — MARQUEE STRIP (font-display + étoiles gold)
   ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
<div class="marquee-strip" data-controller="marquee" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="marquee-strip-track" data-marquee-target="track">
        <span class="marquee-strip-item">9-12h <em>récupérées par semaine</em></span>
        <span class="marquee-strip-star">★</span>
        <span class="marquee-strip-item">3 Agents <em>opérationnels</em></span>
        <span class="marquee-strip-star">★</span>
        <span class="marquee-strip-item">Méthode P.R.O.M.P.T.</span>
        <span class="marquee-strip-star">★</span>
        <span class="marquee-strip-item">147€ <em>early-bird</em></span>
        <span class="marquee-strip-star">★</span>
        <span class="marquee-strip-item">Garantie <em>14 jours</em></span>
        <span class="marquee-strip-star">★</span>
    </div>
</div>

{# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
   SECTION 3 — INTRO + STATS BAR
   ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ #}
<section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="padding: 8rem 2.5rem;">
    <span class="editorial-number left" aria-hidden="true">01</span>

    <div class="relative z-10" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: end; max-width: 1240px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div class="reveal-left intro-grid-left">
            <span class="deco-asterisk" aria-hidden="true">*</span>
            <div class="eyebrow-ds">À propos · Rama</div>
            <h2 class="section-title-ds split" data-controller="split-text">
                Pour les solos qui veulent <em>scaler</em>.<br>Sans recruter.
            </h2>
            <span class="rule-draw" style="max-width: 280px; margin-top: 1.5rem;"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal-right delay-2 intro-grid-right">
            <p class="has-dropcap" style="font-size: var(--text-lg); color: var(--fg-muted); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed); max-width: 56ch;">
                Je suis Rama Soumaré, formatrice IA. Depuis 2 ans, j'aide les consultants, formateurs et coachs solo non-tech à intégrer Claude dans leur quotidien. Pas avec des promesses floues — avec des prompts, des agents, des workflows qui tournent.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: var(--text-lg); color: var(--fg-muted); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed); margin-top: 1rem;">
                <span style="color: var(--color-gold-500); font-style: italic; font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--text-xl);">Pas de blabla. Que de l'action.</span>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-bar" style="max-width: 1240px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
        <div class="stat reveal">
            <span class="stat-num"
                  data-controller="counter-animation"
                  data-counter-animation-target-value="150"
                  data-counter-animation-suffix-value="+">+0</span>
            <div class="stat-label">[PLACEHOLDER] Élèves accompagnés</div>
            <p class="stat-helper">Solopreneurs qui ont intégré Claude dans leur quotidien.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat reveal delay-2">
            <span class="stat-num"
                  data-controller="counter-animation"
                  data-counter-animation-target-value="11"
                  data-counter-animation-suffix-value="h">0h</span>
            <div class="stat-label">Gagnées / semaine</div>
            <p class="stat-helper">Moyenne après 14 jours d'application des 3 Agents.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat reveal delay-3">
            <span class="stat-num"
                  data-controller="counter-animation"
                  data-counter-animation-target-value="98"
                  data-counter-animation-suffix-value="%">0%</span>
            <div class="stat-label">[PLACEHOLDER] Recommandent</div>
            <p class="stat-helper">À un confrère, sur les avis post-formation.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

